| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3115 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2659b235-d3f8-5367-a1a6-2b2ed0adf072"
